{
  "video_id": "qGIBN2gEIeU",
  "title": "Joseph Lekuton: A parable for Kenya",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 18330.0,
      "end_time": 21305.0,
      "text": "My name is Joseph, a Member of Parliament in Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 21330.0,
      "end_time": 23305.0,
      "text": "Picture a Maasai village,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23329.0,
      "end_time": 24496.0,
      "text": "and one evening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24909.0,
      "end_time": 27305.0,
      "text": "government soldiers come, surround the village"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27330.0,
      "end_time": 29520.0,
      "text": "and ask each elder to bring one boy to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29545.0,
      "end_time": 31306.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how I went to school --"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31330.0,
      "end_time": 33330.0,
      "text": "pretty much a government guy pointing a gun"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33354.0,
      "end_time": 35593.0,
      "text": "and told my father, \"You have to make a choice.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35617.0,
      "end_time": 38306.0,
      "text": "I walked very comfortably to this missionary school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38330.0,
      "end_time": 40306.0,
      "text": "that was run by an American missionary."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40330.0,
      "end_time": 43306.0,
      "text": "The first thing the American missionary gave me was a candy."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43330.0,
      "end_time": 45306.0,
      "text": "I had never in my life ever tasted candy."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45330.0,
      "end_time": 47949.0,
      "text": "So I said to myself, with all these hundred other boys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47974.0,
      "end_time": 49334.0,
      "text": "this is where I belong."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49360.0,
      "end_time": 51161.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) I stayed."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51186.0,
      "end_time": 53306.0,
      "text": "When everybody else was dropping out."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53330.0,
      "end_time": 55500.0,
      "text": "My family moved; we&#39;re nomads."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55750.0,
      "end_time": 57270.0,
      "text": "It was a boarding school, I was seven --"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57520.0,
      "end_time": 59740.0,
      "text": "Every time it closed you had to travel to find them."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59765.0,
      "end_time": 61306.0,
      "text": "40-50 miles, it doesn&#39;t matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61330.0,
      "end_time": 63330.0,
      "text": "You slept in the bush, but you kept going."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63849.0,
      "end_time": 66306.0,
      "text": "And I stayed. I don&#39;t know why, but I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66330.0,
      "end_time": 70306.0,
      "text": "All of a sudden I passed the national examination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70330.0,
      "end_time": 73306.0,
      "text": "found myself in a very beautiful high school in Kenya."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73330.0,
      "end_time": 75820.0,
      "text": "And I finished high school."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75238.0,
      "end_time": 77540.0,
      "text": "And just walking, I found a man"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77800.0,
      "end_time": 79679.0,
      "text": "who gave me a full scholarship to the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79947.0,
      "end_time": 81964.0,
      "text": "My mother still lived in a cow-dung hut,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 81989.0,
      "end_time": 84110.0,
      "text": "none of my brothers were going to school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84360.0,
      "end_time": 86306.0,
      "text": "and this man told me, \"Here, go.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86330.0,
      "end_time": 87365.0,
      "text": "I got a scholarship"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87389.0,
      "end_time": 90270.0,
      "text": "to St. Lawrence University, Upstate New York;"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90530.0,
      "end_time": 91920.0,
      "text": "finished that."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 91655.0,
      "end_time": 95255.0,
      "text": "And after that I went to Harvard Graduate School;"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95330.0,
      "end_time": 96518.0,
      "text": "finished that."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97400.0,
      "end_time": 98726.0,
      "text": "Then I worked in DC a little bit:"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98751.0,
      "end_time": 101812.0,
      "text": "I wrote a book for National Geographic and taught U.S. history."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101837.0,
      "end_time": 104306.0,
      "text": "And every time, I kept going back home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 104487.0,
      "end_time": 105955.0,
      "text": "listening to their problems --"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 105980.0,
      "end_time": 108525.0,
      "text": "sick people, people with no water, all this stuff --"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 108550.0,
      "end_time": 110134.0,
      "text": "every time I go back to America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110494.0,
      "end_time": 111945.0,
      "text": "I kept thinking about them."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 111970.0,
      "end_time": 115800.0,
      "text": "Then one day, an elder gave me a story that went like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 115695.0,
      "end_time": 119592.0,
      "text": "long time ago, there was a big war between tribes."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119854.0,
      "end_time": 123304.0,
      "text": "This specific tribe was really afraid of this other Luhya tribe."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123330.0,
      "end_time": 126411.0,
      "text": "Every time, they sent scouts to make sure no one attacked them."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 126894.0,
      "end_time": 129857.0,
      "text": "So one day, the scouts came running and told the villagers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 129882.0,
      "end_time": 133250.0,
      "text": "\"The enemies are coming. Only half an hour away, they&#39;ll be here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 133830.0,
      "end_time": 136563.0,
      "text": "So people scrambled, took their things and ready to go, move out."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 136909.0,
      "end_time": 138635.0,
      "text": "But there were two men:"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 138660.0,
      "end_time": 141128.0,
      "text": "one man was blind, one man had no legs"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 141152.0,
      "end_time": 142456.0,
      "text": "-- he was born like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 142481.0,
      "end_time": 146378.0,
      "text": "The leader of the chiefs said, \"No, sorry. We can&#39;t take you. You&#39;ll slow us down."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 146402.0,
      "end_time": 149892.0,
      "text": "We have to flee our women and children, we have to run.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150648.0,
      "end_time": 153370.0,
      "text": "And they were left behind, waiting to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 153330.0,
      "end_time": 156305.0,
      "text": "But these two people worked something out."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 156330.0,
      "end_time": 159473.0,
      "text": "The blind man said, \"Look, I&#39;m a very strong man but I can&#39;t see.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 159497.0,
      "end_time": 162783.0,
      "text": "The man with no legs says, \"I can see as far as the end of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 162807.0,
      "end_time": 167305.0,
      "text": "but I can&#39;t save myself from a cat, or whatever animals.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 167925.0,
      "end_time": 171306.0,
      "text": "The blind man went down on his knees like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 171330.0,
      "end_time": 174378.0,
      "text": "and told the man with no legs to go over his back, and stood up."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 174710.0,
      "end_time": 177306.0,
      "text": "The man on top can see, the blind man can walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 178121.0,
      "end_time": 180977.0,
      "text": "These guys took off, followed the footsteps of the villagers"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 181200.0,
      "end_time": 183680.0,
      "text": "until they found and passed them."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 185330.0,
      "end_time": 189306.0,
      "text": "So, this was told to me in a setup of elders."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 189330.0,
      "end_time": 191250.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s a really poor area."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 191490.0,
      "end_time": 192504.0,
      "text": "I represent Northern Kenya:"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 192529.0,
      "end_time": 195830.0,
      "text": "the most nomadic, remote areas you can even find."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 196330.0,
      "end_time": 198306.0,
      "text": "And that man told me, \"So, here you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 198330.0,
      "end_time": 201822.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve got a good education from America, you have a good life in America;"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 202298.0,
      "end_time": 204930.0,
      "text": "what are you going to do for us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 205417.0,
      "end_time": 208306.0,
      "text": "We want you to be our eyes, we&#39;ll give you the legs."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 208330.0,
      "end_time": 210306.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll walk you, you lead us.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 210742.0,
      "end_time": 213351.0,
      "text": "The opportunity came. I was always thinking about that:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 213376.0,
      "end_time": 215306.0,
      "text": "\"What can I do to help my people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 215330.0,
      "end_time": 218676.0,
      "text": "Every time you go to an area where for 43 years of independence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 218701.0,
      "end_time": 221242.0,
      "text": "we still don&#39;t have basic health facilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 221267.0,
      "end_time": 224393.0,
      "text": "A man has to be transported in a wheelbarrow 30 km for a hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 224418.0,
      "end_time": 225703.0,
      "text": "No clean drinking water."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 226300.0,
      "end_time": 228305.0,
      "text": "So I said, \"I&#39;m going to dedicate myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 228330.0,
      "end_time": 229576.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m leaving America."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 229901.0,
      "end_time": 231409.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to run for office.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 231734.0,
      "end_time": 234957.0,
      "text": "Last June, I moved from America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 235559.0,
      "end_time": 238395.0,
      "text": "ran in July election and won."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 238933.0,
      "end_time": 241767.0,
      "text": "And I came for them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 242457.0,
      "end_time": 243583.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s my goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 243608.0,
      "end_time": 246400.0,
      "text": "Right now I have in place, for the last nine months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 247155.0,
      "end_time": 249910.0,
      "text": "a plan that in five years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 250370.0,
      "end_time": 253303.0,
      "text": "every nomad will have clean drinking water."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 253774.0,
      "end_time": 256750.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re building dispensaries across that constituency."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 257820.0,
      "end_time": 260480.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m asking my friends from America to help"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 260740.0,
      "end_time": 262306.0,
      "text": "with bringing nurses or doctors to help us out."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 262621.0,
      "end_time": 264664.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m trying to improve infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 265266.0,
      "end_time": 267981.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m using the knowledge I received from the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 268600.0,
      "end_time": 269510.0,
      "text": "and from my community"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 269658.0,
      "end_time": 271580.0,
      "text": "to move them forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 271830.0,
      "end_time": 274540.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m trying to develop homegrown solutions to our issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 274565.0,
      "end_time": 277130.0,
      "text": "because people from outside can come and help us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 277155.0,
      "end_time": 279748.0,
      "text": "but if we don&#39;t help ourselves, there&#39;s nothing to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 280258.0,
      "end_time": 281344.0,
      "text": "My plan right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 281370.0,
      "end_time": 285304.0,
      "text": "as I continue with introducing students to different fields --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 285330.0,
      "end_time": 287179.0,
      "text": "some become doctors, some lawyers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 287204.0,
      "end_time": 289599.0,
      "text": "we want to produce a comprehensive group of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 289624.0,
      "end_time": 292479.0,
      "text": "students who can come back and help us see a community grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 292504.0,
      "end_time": 295812.0,
      "text": "that is in the middle of a huge economic recession."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 296147.0,
      "end_time": 298938.0,
      "text": "As I continue to be a Member of Parliament"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 298964.0,
      "end_time": 302330.0,
      "text": "and as I continue listening to all of you talking about botany,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 302354.0,
      "end_time": 305330.0,
      "text": "health, democracy, new inventions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 305809.0,
      "end_time": 308306.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m hoping that one day in my own little community --"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 308330.0,
      "end_time": 310306.0,
      "text": "which is 26,000 square km,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 310330.0,
      "end_time": 312197.0,
      "text": "maybe five times Rhode Island --"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 312491.0,
      "end_time": 313491.0,
      "text": "with no roads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 313980.0,
      "end_time": 317909.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll be able to become a model to help others develop."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 317933.0,
      "end_time": 319294.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 319318.0,
      "end_time": 320318.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}